Banana Pong

Pong witha banananana

Game descripition

This is a quick and fun one person game.
The goal of the game is to hit moving square with your moving paddle and keep a rally going with the moving paddle on the other side of the screen.

Game objective

The goal of the game is to hit the moving square controling your paddle and for the square to end up getting passed the paddle on the other side of the screen.

Game Rules

There arent many rules in this game.
The game is very restrictive, you can only move up and down. not much can go wrong.
